{"tid":1100042,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"個新娘唔比佢老公出鏡","createTime":"2019-04-10T07:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T18:08:04.000Z","uid":11779,"like":32,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4083cf7d5027bc88650553708a82c55fb01e204f","tid":1100042,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:25:11.000Z","msg":"話說我係大阪幫對新人影啦，咁我地朝早襯人少起身 好早果啲 太陽未出就要去影，咁早餐去居酒屋食。<br />\n點知個新郎對蝦過敏，成塊面生晒粒粒，咁今次仆街啦，係紅到爛面果種，咁個化妝師都好盡力咁幫佢遮但都好明顯。<br />\n<br />\n點知要影時.....<br />\n<br />\n個新娘叫佢老公唔好影 影佢一個就得。<br />\n屌！我係男人都想立即幫個新郎屌爆佢....但個新郎都話冇問題....屌 佢係咪男人黎ga......<br />\n<br />\n香港做男人好慘....連婚攝都要睇女人面色<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d48593d42bc1746fd5d6c7bf310599979f3f00e","tid":1100042,"uid":20291,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:07:02.000Z","msg":"騎牛搵馬你明既。"},{"pid":"b831118fd623ed588903418326617cc1c916c7ca","tid":1100042,"uid":107927,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:11:50.000Z","msg":"個男人可能心諗: 其實唔影我我仲開心"},{"pid":"01d7f614b3f1514ad6b45b771f2eabbd7191599c","tid":1100042,"uid":19712,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"影完PS"},{"pid":"c7533a9c34095587349c0f6a35b8a959e6ad3b83","tid":1100042,"uid":99700,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:12:49.000Z","msg":"正呀 我都唔想結婚"},{"pid":"475ea7e80d38baf9e7e80de4a7c8af9ad0353c14","tid":1100042,"uid":66365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:18:20.000Z","msg":"咁樣衰企開啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075200f2928a0e261c4e555f855090824f3dcf2b","tid":1100042,"uid":33874,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"影結婚相我老婆影得好興奮<br />\n我一心諗幾時放飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實會唔會係個新朗陰謀嚟"},{"pid":"db83e5c70d14298ee738398447fecdda326c8585","tid":1100042,"uid"